{"tid":246103,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"皇馬將續約施丹至2020","createTime":"2017-05-16T17:43:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-03T03:11:37.000Z","uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2debf224f0f63172349ec5bdd22b3a70d7e94ca1","tid":246103,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T17:43:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2017/05/15/0/0fb5cd187c8591387afc279010a820be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F0%2F0fb5cd187c8591387afc279010a820be.jpg&h=2c46d1e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n施丹被曝即將續約<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2017/05/15/c/c5098ba8b0fc22b39f3baaa4f7dd133b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2Fc%2Fc5098ba8b0fc22b39f3baaa4f7dd133b.jpg&h=5017774c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://soccer.sina.com.hk/news/87/20170515/7406999/2.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsoccer.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2F87%2F20170515%2F7406999%2F2.html&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=ae4b8016\" target=\"_blank\">http://soccer.sina.com.hk/news/87/20170515/7406999/2.html</a><br />\n<br />\n《馬卡報》：皇馬將續約施丹至2020年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據《馬卡報》報導，皇馬即將同球隊教練施丹完成續約，雙方將會將合約延長到2020年的6月30日。<br />\n<br />\n《馬卡報》表示，續約是皇馬主席佩雷斯的意思，這份新合同已經放到了施丹的辦公桌上，只要施丹願意，他隨時就能同球隊完成續約。雙方此前的合約將在2018年6月30日到期，鑒於施丹接手以來球隊成績良好，因此皇馬高層和更衣室對施丹都非常滿意，都希望施丹能夠留下，同球隊進行續約。<br />\n<br />\n《馬卡報》還強調，即使施丹這個賽季最終四大皆空，皇馬方面也會同他進行續約。施丹在去年正式接任皇馬教練，並且率隊贏得了歐冠盃、歐洲超級盃和世冠盃，現在又非常有希望贏下西甲聯賽和歐冠盃的冠軍。皇馬上下現在對施丹都非常信任，因此希望能夠用新合約讓他留下來。<br />\n<br />\n不過在之前的新聞記者會上，施丹在回答此類問題時，一直在表示，自己能否留在皇馬，要靠球隊的成績來決定。而從現在的情況來看，他似乎不用考慮這個問題了。"},{"pid":"1243d06f5c652f1cff7f9b910daed156ba26729c","tid":246103,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T19:30:57.000Z","msg":"樂觀SIR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509d97557ed5fb5e00223fddf74fe58e65a334a1","tid":246103,"uid":53378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T19:35:55.000Z","msg":"永續又點<br />\n下季一樣可以用解約金踢走你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b5e2df8e674e27c957dc12cc6144300df1c85d","tid":246103,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T19:36:42.000Z","msg":"Zidane<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6bde5ed139e96040cd997f9268154c9b5c9445d","tid":246103,"uid":37465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T00:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2cdd9cd9aa17f62c6c6233dcbe81a06f1dc8415","tid":246103,"uid":22866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T00:39:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>永續又點<br />\n下季一樣可以用解約金踢走你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔駛下季，歐聯輸俾祖記就即刻玩撚猿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b150a90b81f4842472f9e00d9e723696b538b2ad","tid":246103,"uid":4028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T00:42:21.000Z","msg":"施丹同賓周馬有路<br />\n賓周馬同法國總統馬卡龍有路<br />\n佩雷斯搞鳩施丹<br />\n法國幫都暴動了"},{"pid":"27b4fa66146233c45fc18b16b7894302560f33ba","tid":246103,"uid":52053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T00:56:14.000Z","msg":"佢幾時會出返出黎踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd820b68207615cff3f85d2ac4d4eb3002ede4a","tid":246103,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T00:57:00.000Z","msg":"教左一季已經超越左雲加"},{"pid":"5953d3e9d8cbdd7f636f11ed73dd5f7cfc1b4842","tid":246103,"uid":37735,"li